.Dd $Mdocdate: February 25 2010 $
.Dt AUGLX 4
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm auglx
.Nd AMD Geode LX CS5536 integrated AC'97 audio device
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Cd "auglx* at pci?"
.Cd "audio* at auglx?"
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Nm
device driver supports the integrated AC'97 audio controller
of the AMD Geode LX CS5536 companion chip.
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr ac97 4 ,
.Xr audio 4 ,
.Xr intro 4 ,
.Xr pci 4
.Sh HISTORY
The
.Nm
device driver first appeared in
.Ox 4.4 .
